## 12. Entity-Relationship Diagram (ERD)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USER ||--o{ FARM : owns
    USER {
        int user_id PK
        string full_name
        string role "Farmer, Officer, Admin"
    }
    
    FARM ||--o{ ZONE : contains
    FARM {
        int farm_id PK
        string farm_name
        float total_area
    }
    
    ZONE ||--o{ PLAN : has
    ZONE {
        int zone_id PK
        geometry polygon_coordinates
        string condition_profile
    }

    CROP ||--o{ COMPANION_MATRIX : relates_to
    CROP {
        int crop_id PK
        string crop_name
        float optimal_ph
    }
    
    COMPANION_MATRIX {
        int crop_id_1 FK
        int crop_id_2 FK
        int compatibility_score
    }

    PLAN ||--o{ TASK : generates
    PLAN {
        int plan_id PK
        float simulated_ler
    }

    TASK {
        int task_id PK
        string task_type
        date due_date
        string status
    }
```
